data.title: Clubs that have attained The Safeguarding Code in Martial Arts in England
meta_keywords: Clubs that have attained The Safeguarding Code in Martial Arts in England
data.text:
The providers on this map have attained the Safeguarding Code in Martial Arts. This is a great way to know a martial arts provider is committed to safeguarding. We all have a role to play in safeguarding to help ensure children have a great experience.

The search criteria below provides an opportunity for parents and carers to discover martial arts clubs, local to you, that have attained the Safeguarding Code. Search criteria such as postcode, martial art or distance, can help you find the most relevant clubs to where you live.
